    (1) The land hereinafter described is hereby set apart for the development of water-power (Horahora scheme).
    
    (2) The sum of four thousand seven hundred and ninety-six dollars and twenty-five cents shall be transferred from the Electric-supply Account to the Consolidated Fund as consideration for such transfer.
    
    (3) The land to which subsection [one][101] hereof relates is particularly described as follows:---
    
