    (2) The Otautau Town Board is hereby empowered to refund to the persons entitled such sums as were paid by those persons as members of the Otautau Town Board pursuant to a surcharge by the Audit Office on the members of the Otautau Town Board in respect of the said sum of seventeen dollars and twenty and five-sixths cents.
    
